# P4-003: Genotype filter pushdown — af_range, ac_range, genotype_range

Issue: Scan-level genotype filtering for biobank-scale rare variant queries.

## Status

- [ ] Phase 1: `af_range` + `ac_range` variant-level filtering
- [ ] Phase 2: `genotype_range` row/element-level filtering
- [ ] Phase 3: Test fixtures (1K×100, 30K×1K) and scale tests

