## Future Work (Out of Scope)

- **DuckDB filter pushdown**: consume WHERE clause predicates via
  `pushdown_complex_filter` or `filter_pushdown = true` to automatically
  apply these filters without explicit parameters
- **`genotypes := 'struct'`**: single STRUCT column with named subfields;
  genotype_range would skip fields (named, not positional — struct fields
  are resolved at bind time but could be filtered if the struct is built
  dynamically per variant)
- **Parallel genotype orient**: multi-threaded scan for `orient := 'genotype'`
  (same architecture as variant orient with inner sample unnest)
- **`include_missing` parameter**: opt-in to include missing genotypes when
  filters are active
- **Dosage-aware AF**: use `PgrGetDCounts` for dosage-based allele frequency
  instead of hard-call counts
- **Dosage genotype_range**: continuous 0.0–2.0 filtering (depends on P4-002)
